18 July 2012In honour of Mandela Day the post-Cabinet media briefing scheduled for this afternoon has been postponed.Cabinet Spokesperson, Mr Jimmy Manyi will address members of the media on the outcomes of the Cabinet meeting held on 17 July 2012 on Thursday, 19 July.The Director-General of the Department of Sport and Recreation South Africa, Mr Alec Moemi, will also provide an update on 2013 AFCON matters at this briefing.The details are as follows:Date: Thursday, 19 July 2012 Time: 11h00 Venue: GCIS Auditorium, 1st Floor, Midtown Building, cnr Sisulu and Madiba Streets, Pretoria RSVP: Proffesor Ndawonde (Pretoria) E-mail: proffesor@gcis.gov.za Cell 073 597 9534 Sbongile Dalasile (Cape Town) E-mail: sbongile@gcis.gov.za Cell: 0712921006Enquiries: Jimmy Manyi Cell: 082 379 3454Issued by: Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)